tier0
    - test suite self-check
    - LABEL: tier0

tier1
    - smoke tests (basic functionality)
    - LABEL: tier1

tier2
    - remaining, non-destructive tests
    - LABEL: no label, a default tier

tier3
    - test on a live system
    - tests with bash scriptlets
    - test more complex scenarios with http, ftp repos, proxy, etc.
    - LABEL: tier3
